UNK iz gevorn di milkhome. fun der milkhome nit dertseyln, nor fun zikh. VSYO.

00:04:22.750 --> 00:04:26.002
dertseylt, vu hot ir zikh geboyrn?

00:04:23.746 --> 00:04:26.030
 iz geven...

00:04:26.030 --> 00:04:29.005
ikh bin geboyrn gevorn in Meskivke,

00:04:30.192 --> 00:04:33.258
toyznt nayn hundert finef un tsvontsiktn yor.

00:04:33.820 --> 00:04:37.797
dertseylt, vos iz geven, a shtetl

00:04:37.989 --> 00:04:39.400
Meskivke?

00:04:39.153 --> 00:04:40.396
a shtetl.

00:04:40.486 --> 00:04:42.337
dertseylt, a sakh.

00:04:41.583 --> 00:04:45.003
Krizhopilsker rayon, a shtetlke.

00:04:45.127 --> 00:04:49.829
ibergelebt hot men genug. DO VOINY hobn mir gornit ibergelebt.

00:04:53.902 --> 00:04:54.571
gut.

00:04:54.914 --> 00:04:56.022
KHOROSHO.

00:04:57.800 --> 00:05:00.421
dertseylt, vifl geven dortn

00:05:01.175 --> 00:05:04.038
shtiber, vifl hobn gevoynt yidn.

00:05:03.369 --> 00:05:10.175
yidn, mistam bay di, dray hundert SEMEISTVOs geze- geve- gezesn.

00:05:10.203 --> 00:05:12.864
bay undz in Mo- in, in Meskivke.

00:05:16.194 --> 00:05:19.158
ve- mit vos hot zikh ge- di yidn

00:05:19.265 --> 00:05:22.027
ge- farnemen?

00:05:20.547 --> 00:05:21.532
ye-

00:05:21.560 --> 00:05:29.300
ve- yeder hot zikh gehat zayn SPETSIAL'NOST'; der hot, geneyt, der iz a shuster geven, der a shnayder geven,

00:05:29.575 --> 00:05:32.686
un der hot gearbet in a kleyt.

00:05:32.686 --> 00:05:36.100
s'iz o- yeder mentsh hot zikh gehat zayn

00:05:36.410 --> 00:05:39.054
zayn SPOSOBNOST' tsu zayn arbet.

00:05:42.400 --> 00:05:44.200
ir dertseylt, dertseylt.

00:05:43.683 --> 00:05:47.563
ikh dertseyl dos vos yeder hot gearbet.

00:05:48.409 --> 00:05:55.831
der hot azoy gearbet, der hot azoy gearbet. nu, mir ho- yeder hot gehat zayn ZABOTA. zayn arbet, zayn ZABOTA.

00:05:57.385 --> 00:06:00.112
vos iz geven, dortn

00:06:00.112 --> 00:06:04.484
ZAVODY, fabrikes, s'iz geven, vos iz geven dortn?

00:06:02.364 --> 00:06:06.273
ne-, keyn ZAVO- nit geven, UNK iz geven.

00:06:08.506 --> 00:06:12.230
a yidishe shkole, a rusishe shkole, ukrainishe.

00:06:12.320 --> 00:06:14.451
vayter azoy iz gornit geven bay undz.

00:06:14.693 --> 00:06:18.760
a teyl ze'mir &lt;raykh ven do a KONSERVNYI ZAVOD&gt;, bay undz iz nit geven.

00:06:19.627 --> 00:06:20.924
Meskivke.

00:06:22.732 --> 00:06:28.194
nu, dertseylt, ir gedenkt ayer bobe, di, di zeydn?

00:06:27.069 --> 00:06:31.552
di bobe Genye iz dokh, gedenk ikh azoy vi durkhn shlof.

00:06:32.722 --> 00:06:34.707
vemes iz dos mame geven?

00:06:34.612 --> 00:06:36.800
es iz dem tatn's mame.

00:06:36.046 --> 00:06:38.082
nu dertseylt, vos f-, vos ke-

00:06:37.194 --> 00:06:39.129
iz der tatn's mame.

00:06:41.142 --> 00:06:45.560
me, iz nokh fun far der milkhome geke- iz zi gezesn mit a tokhter.

00:06:45.560 --> 00:06:49.087
 di tokhter hot keyn man nit gehat, keyn kinder nit gehat.

00:06:49.087 --> 00:06:54.490
iz, iz, iz, hobn banditn ongefaln oyf ir.

00:06:54.490 --> 00:06:58.560
m'hot zi tseklapt, iz zi gelign in BOL'NITSA, un di mume Leye.

00:06:59.317 --> 00:07:00.509
s'iz geven

00:07:00.582 --> 00:07:03.091
 oykhet PEREZHIVANIE.

00:07:06.826 --> 00:07:08.238
dem zeydn?

00:07:08.328 --> 00:07:12.696
der zeyde, der zeyde iz nit geven; nor di bobe geven mit der,

00:07:12.696 --> 00:07:15.123
me- iz zi gezesn mit a tokhter.

00:07:16.597 --> 00:07:17.902
gedenk...

00:07:16.691 --> 00:07:17.901
vemes...

00:07:17.902 --> 00:07:19.598
mayn ma- mayn tatn's

00:07:19.598 --> 00:07:22.599
shvester un mayn tatn's mame.

00:07:23.549 --> 00:07:27.357
un der, un der zeyde iz shoyn fun lang geshtorbn.

00:07:29.624 --> 00:07:30.800
der zeyde

00:07:31.835 --> 00:07:33.804
iz shoyn fun lang geshtorbn.

00:07:34.045 --> 00:07:37.027
iz geblibn di bobe Genye mit der TETIA.

00:07:38.619 --> 00:07:39.963
un azoy...

00:07:40.323 --> 00:07:42.562
un der tate hot gearbet.

00:07:42.804 --> 00:07:45.194
yeder hot zikh gehat zayn ZABOTA.

00:07:46.449 --> 00:07:50.631
nu, dem zeydn fun der t-, der der tate's tate

00:07:50.634 --> 00:07:51.489
gedenkt?

00:07:51.477 --> 00:07:53.609
neyn, neyn. ikh gedenk...

00:07:52.169 --> 00:07:53.632
vi azoy hot men im geheysn?

00:07:53.609 --> 00:07:54.357
ah?

00:07:54.599 --> 00:07:56.264
er hot geheysn Shmerl.

00:07:58.126 --> 00:07:59.875
mayn tate hot geheysn Velvl.

00:08:01.147 --> 00:08:04.502
mit vos hot zikh, der zeyde, Shmerl,

00:08:04.502 --> 00:08:06.406
vos hot er getun?

00:08:06.142 --> 00:08:10.606
vos er hot getun? er iz oykhet, gearbet in a organizatsye

00:08:10.606 --> 00:08:13.220
in &lt;hot ZAGOTOVet&gt;, geforn in dorf,

00:08:13.220 --> 00:08:15.536
felekhlekh, &lt;krolikes&gt;

00:08:15.536 --> 00:08:20.238
azoy fun, fun &lt;a ku&gt; di felekhlekh

00:08:21.599 --> 00:08:24.004
un mayn tate hot oykhet gehandlt.

00:08:25.784 --> 00:08:27.415
nu, vos heyst, er hot ge-

00:08:26.442 --> 00:08:28.220
er hot ge-, er hot gehandlt.

00:08:28.220 --> 00:08:30.256
to nokh dem der DYADYA Srol,

00:08:30.256 --> 00:08:34.081
zey farnemen dem DYADYA Yosl un mayn tatn keyn Zhmerinke

00:08:34.081 --> 00:08:35.940
az zey zoln forn keyn Tambov,

00:08:35.940 --> 00:08:39.168
ZAGOTOVen peltsn alte.

00:08:39.168 --> 00:08:42.537
flegn zey forn, far der milkhome iz dos geven.

00:08:43.284 --> 00:08:45.303
 hobn zey gearbet.

00:08:47.604 --> 00:08:48.850
hobn zey gearbet.

00:08:48.850 --> 00:08:51.247
der DYADYA Yosl, der DYADYA Srol

00:08:51.247 --> 00:08:53.462
zenen avekgeforn, hobn zikh gekent

00:08:53.462 --> 00:08:58.983
z-, gedovern mistam tsvey dray khadoshim biz vanen zey zenen gekumen.

00:08:58.983 --> 00:09:00.080
un gelt

00:09:00.125 --> 00:09:04.257
hot men zey gegibn fun Zhmerinke a SPRAVKA vi zey zenen arayngegan,

00:09:04.257 --> 00:09:06.116
az s'hot zikh nit USTAYet keyn gelt,

00:09:06.116 --> 00:09:09.643
un oyf velkhe bank zey zenen arayngegan hot men zey gegibn gelt

00:09:09.643 --> 00:09:11.240
vifl zey hobn gedarft.

00:09:12.072 --> 00:09:13.752
mayn tate olevasholem fleg der-

00:09:13.752 --> 00:09:14.784
dertseyln.

00:09:17.506 --> 00:09:20.875
ir hot gezogt der zeyde iz ge- iz

00:09:21.016 --> 00:09:22.574
di felekhlekh

00:09:22.585 --> 00:09:23.899
hot er genemen.

00:09:23.899 --> 00:09:26.815
vu hot er genemen, vi azoy hot er zey genemen?

00:09:23.936 --> 00:09:25.189
yo!

00:09:25.503 --> 00:09:33.181
 er iz, er iz gegan in dorf arayn, ele nit, goyim flegn brengen in shtub arayn a felekhl un er fleg koyfn,

00:09:33.181 --> 00:09:36.447
fleg onkoyfn a tsvey dray zeklekh, opfirn keyn Krizhopil.

00:09:36.447 --> 00:09:39.868
azoy iz mayn zeyde geven. azoy iz der, der tate geven.

00:09:39.868 --> 00:09:43.026
dem zeydn gedenk ikh nit. nor di bobe gedenk ikh.

00:09:43.026 --> 00:09:46.130
dem zeydn, nit far mir geven.

00:09:46.126 --> 00:09:48.247
ver hot gemakht di peltsn?

00:09:48.877 --> 00:09:51.023
ver hot gemakht?

00:09:51.023 --> 00:09:58.692
ZAGOTOVet peltsn in, in Tambov un me fleg shikn TYUKn peltsn in Zhmerinke in ARTEL',

00:09:58.727 --> 00:10:04.517
un in ARTEL' gezesn mentshn un m'hot gearbet, un m'hot gemakht fun der hoyt a naye.

00:10:07.945 --> 00:10:10.238
mayn tate hot gearbet far der milkhome.

00:10:10.238 --> 00:10:11.284
iz oykhet

00:10:11.284 --> 00:10:13.823
der DYADYA Srol hot er genemen

00:10:13.823 --> 00:10:17.095
say dem DYADYA Yosl un say mayn tatn, un m'hot gearbet.

00:10:18.475 --> 00:10:20.343
nu, dertseylt fun der mame.

00:10:20.754 --> 00:10:23.611
iz di mame geven a DOMASHNe baleboste.

00:10:23.611 --> 00:10:25.585
geven, kinder,

00:10:25.585 --> 00:10:29.017
geven a DOMASHNe baleboste. geroymt, gekokht, ge-

00:10:29.613 --> 00:10:31.227
alts hot zi getun.

00:10:32.279 --> 00:10:36.256
fleg aleyn shmirn, fleg vashn un fleg ales tun.

00:10:36.380 --> 00:10:37.454
un

00:10:38.118 --> 00:10:42.500
UNK &lt;azoy hobn mir&gt; mir hobn gelebt gvirish. azoy o, UNK.

00:10:44.125 --> 00:10:46.854
nu, dertseylt, fun ayer shtub.

00:10:47.551 --> 00:10:49.334
in in in undzer shtub

00:10:49.694 --> 00:10:52.405
iz geven dray KOMNATn mit a kikh.

00:10:52.546 --> 00:10:54.127
ze'mir gezesn.

00:10:54.790 --> 00:10:56.439
geven a gute shtub.

00:10:57.862 --> 00:10:59.937
untn in magzon hobn mir

00:10:59.937 --> 00:11:03.962
hot der tate gehaltn dos ferd mitn &lt;furlekh, ayngeforn&gt;,

00:11:03.962 --> 00:11:06.407
azoy iz gekumen funem dorf.

00:11:07.919 --> 00:11:08.926
un shoyn,

00:11:09.286 --> 00:11:10.209
mir hobn

00:11:10.889 --> 00:11:12.713
un m'hot azoy gelebt.

00:11:13.674 --> 00:11:15.127
vos hot men gekent?

00:11:14.889 --> 00:11:18.269
vos iz geven, vos iz geshteln bay aykh in in sh-

00:11:18.649 --> 00:11:23.109
vi, az mir hobn gehat fun vanet hobn mir &lt;di zal&gt; oysge-

00:11:23.109 --> 00:11:29.718
mit mebl, gekoyft a naye shafe un a bufet un a tish mit benklekh, mit ales.

00:11:29.718 --> 00:11:33.343
in alker iz geshtanen tsvey betn mit a alter shafe.

00:11:33.343 --> 00:11:39.343
in shtub iz geshtanen nokh a shafe mit a tish mit benklekh mit a bufetl.

00:11:40.167 --> 00:11:41.174
azoy o.

00:11:42.985 --> 00:11:47.182
un in kikh iz geshtanen azoy vi in a kikh.

00:11:47.474 --> 00:11:50.607
in alker iz geshtanen tsvey betn mit a shafe.

00:11:54.055 --> 00:11:57.442
vu hot ir genemen vaser? vi azoy hot ir zikh gevashn?

00:11:56.350 --> 00:11:58.657
vaser iz bayn undz geven a kernitse.

00:11:59.472 --> 00:12:02.414
geven a kernitse, eyn kernitse in shtot.

00:12:02.442 --> 00:12:08.701
un zeyer a tife kernitse; di beste vaser, un kalte vaser iz geven, di beste vaser iz geven.

00:12:08.701 --> 00:12:13.920
az me fleg &lt;darfn&gt; geyn nemen an emer vaser hot men gedarft shteyn in otshered

00:12:13.920 --> 00:12:15.599
nokhn emer vaser.

00:12:17.242 --> 00:12:20.108
un di mame hot zikh demolt oysgebrokhn a &lt;hant&gt;

00:12:20.108 --> 00:12:23.497
fle- fleg zi geyn frier farnemen a otshered

00:12:23.857 --> 00:12:27.813
un, un, un ikh bin mitn,

00:12:27.813 --> 00:12:32.188
mitn shvesterl gezesn. der bruder iz nit geven; er iz geven in der ARMIIA.

00:12:32.188 --> 00:12:34.485
bin ikh mitn shvesterl gezesn.

00:12:34.505 --> 00:12:40.380
hob ikh shoyn farshtanen ven di, di mame hot shoyn ongenemen di vaser, bin ikh gegan; kh'hob ir geholfn trogn dem emer vaser.

00:12:40.380 --> 00:12:43.583
un di shvesterl hob ikh ibergelozt in shtub.

00:12:43.583 --> 00:12:48.208
ibergelozt in shtub, iz zi aroysgelofn in ga- oyfn ganik, un hot gebrent.

00:12:48.265 --> 00:12:53.005
ikh hob gegibn a vorf dem, dem emer un gelofn

00:12:53.405 --> 00:12:55.410
gelofn tsum kind,

00:12:55.410 --> 00:12:57.145
vos ikh bin geven a kind.

00:12:57.674 --> 00:12:59.970
hob ikh aropgenemen, s'iz geven osyen,

00:12:59.970 --> 00:13:05.174
aropgevorfn di kufayke un aribergevorfn oyfn kind, hob ikh zi opgeloshn a bisl.

00:13:05.174 --> 00:13:06.899
nor s'iz shoyn geven shpet.

00:13:07.900 --> 00:13:13.306
hot men, iz gekumen SKORAIA POMOSHCH'. m'hot farnumen mayn mame mitn kind keyn

00:13:13.306 --> 00:13:17.259
keyn Marakh- keyn Meskivke; fun Meskivke hot men zi ge-

00:13:17.259 --> 00:13:22.556
gefirt keyn Sha- keyn Krizhopil, un fun Krizhopil hot men zi farfirt keyn

00:13:22.556 --> 00:13:23.470
Tultshin.

00:13:23.594 --> 00:13:27.858
un take in Tultshin iz zi geshtorbn un m'hot, m'hot &lt;es ge-&gt; bahaltn in Tultshin.

00:13:28.707 --> 00:13:30.069
vi azoy hot ir geheysn?

00:13:29.905 --> 00:13:31.807
vi azoy hot geheysn? Rivitshke.

00:13:32.403 --> 00:13:34.692
mayn mame hot gegibn a nomen nokh ir mamen.

00:13:35.896 --> 00:13:38.742
dertseylt vifl iz bay aykh geven

00:13:39.288 --> 00:13:40.244
kinder?

00:13:39.372 --> 00:13:42.614
bay mayn mame, bay mayn mamen iz geven nayn kinder.

00:13:42.614 --> 00:13:44.395
nor ikh mit Rivele,

00:13:44.395 --> 00:13:46.661
mit &lt;Arn, dos&gt; zenen mir geven.

00:13:46.661 --> 00:13:53.489
un di, un di iberike kinder geven biz tsvey yor, biz dray yor hobn zey gelebt un zenen geshtorbn.

00:13:53.834 --> 00:13:58.030
un dernokhdem iz Rivitshke farbrent gevorn, oykhet geven bay undz a slutshay.

00:13:58.374 --> 00:14:00.649
iz bin ikh geven nor mit mayn bruder.

00:14:00.649 --> 00:14:07.945
er iz avekgegan in der ARMIIA. &lt;er&gt; hot nokh gelebt mayn Rivitshke. fleg in yedn briv mayn bruder shraybn "kush Rivitshken"

00:14:07.945 --> 00:14:10.352
geven zeyer a klug meydele.

00:14:10.743 --> 00:14:13.000
a royte nor a klugs.

00:14:13.000 --> 00:14:14.838
a durkhgetribns.

00:14:15.873 --> 00:14:21.385
ikh hob geleg- gelernt do urokn, hot zi gikher gekent fun mir vos ikh hob gelernt.

00:14:21.661 --> 00:14:23.579
aza SPOSOBNOST' iz geven.

00:14:23.551 --> 00:14:24.980
vifl iz geven yor?

00:14:25.104 --> 00:14:28.642
zi iz geven zeks tsi zibn yor, azoy PRIBLIZITEL'NO.

00:14:29.575 --> 00:14:30.262
DA.

00:14:30.689 --> 00:14:32.557
geven zeyer a tayer kind.

00:14:32.731 --> 00:14:33.400
nu

00:14:35.110 --> 00:14:39.188
un mayn tate afile nit gevust; iz er geven tsvey khadoshim in Tambov.

00:14:39.188 --> 00:14:43.906
er hot ibergelozt a gezunt kind un gekumen un, un hot shoyn nit getrofn.

00:14:45.303 --> 00:14:46.867
iz oykhet a

00:14:47.868 --> 00:14:50.512
&lt;iz&gt; geven a tragedye mitn lebn.

00:14:56.947 --> 00:15:00.130
der tate, vos hot nokh geton,

00:15:01.115 --> 00:15:04.925
&lt;in&gt; der ershter tsayt iz geven, iz er geven in Meskivke, hot er

00:15:04.925 --> 00:15:08.053
gearbet in VILSHINKI &lt;in an&gt; organizatsye

00:15:08.053 --> 00:15:11.106
un hot dortn ge- gekoyft felekhlekh

00:15:11.106 --> 00:15:13.148
un hot genemen mitn furl

00:15:13.148 --> 00:15:16.775
shmates opgefirt keyn Krizhopil, felekhlekh, vos er hot

00:15:17.062 --> 00:15:20.721
far- gekoyft hot er opgefirt keyn Krizhopil.

00:15:20.721 --> 00:15:22.796
er iz geven in aza, an organizatsye.

00:15:22.796 --> 00:15:25.243
dernokhdem hot der DYADYA Srol

00:15:25.243 --> 00:15:28.211
genemen mayn tatn un mayn DYADYA Yoslen

00:15:28.211 --> 00:15:32.531
keyn, keyn Zhmerinke un hot, un hot zey ustroyet

00:15:32.531 --> 00:15:35.978
in der, in dem, vu er hot gearbet.

00:15:35.978 --> 00:15:37.764
iz er geforn keyn Tambov.

00:15:37.764 --> 00:15:43.227
iz, der DYADYA Srol, der DYADYA Yosl, un, un der tate mayner, zenen zey geforn

00:15:43.227 --> 00:15:46.398
un zenen geven tsvey dray khadoshim in

00:15:46.398 --> 00:15:48.182
dort in Tambov.

00:15:49.057 --> 00:15:52.275
un in Kr- un in Zhmerinke hot men gegibn a SPRAVKA.

00:15:52.275 --> 00:15:55.340
keyn gelt hot men nit gegibn, nor me hot im gegibn aza SPRAVKA

00:15:55.340 --> 00:16:02.376
&lt;vi&gt; er iz arayngegan in a ba- in avelekh bank iz arayngegan hot men gegibn vifl er hot gedarft hobn gelt, hot men gegibn.

00:16:05.459 --> 00:16:08.626
der tate hot gesluzhet in ARMIIA?

00:16:08.176 --> 00:16:10.244
yo, bay Nikolayen.

00:16:10.244 --> 00:16:13.127
mayn tate hot ge- gesluzhet finef yor.

00:16:13.127 --> 00:16:18.616
un az dernokhdem hot er bay Nikolayen afile... oyf der milkhome geven.

00:16:18.616 --> 00:16:22.148
a mol hot men gedint, yene yorn, finef yor

00:16:22.486 --> 00:16:25.653
tsi zeks yor, azoy o. m'hot lang gedint.

00:16:27.498 --> 00:16:29.770
un dernokhdem hot er UNK

00:16:31.227 --> 00:16:33.095
&lt;s'iz geven&gt; yene yorn.

00:16:33.421 --> 00:16:34.850
vu hot er gedint?

00:16:35.497 --> 00:16:39.734
mayn tate hot gedint in Rige un mayn bruder hot gedint in Rige.

00:16:39.734 --> 00:16:44.330
iz im geve- er ho- er hot finef yor gedint, iz im geven &lt;INTERESNO&gt;.

00:16:44.778 --> 00:16:48.958
mayn mame hot oykhet zeyer ge- gehat, gevolt forn mit mayn tatn

00:16:48.958 --> 00:16:52.149
keyn Rige tsu mayn UNK bruder in der ARMIIA.

00:16:52.149 --> 00:16:55.617
hot der, hot der tate gezogt "oyf vemen vestu iberlozn di kinder?

00:16:55.617 --> 00:16:57.818
un oyf vemen vestu iberlozn di shtub?

00:16:57.818 --> 00:17:01.618
ikh muz forn. iz mir &lt;INTERESNO&gt;, ikh hob gesluzhet,

00:17:01.755 --> 00:17:05.671
ikh veys, dortn; afile bay nakht vel ikh kumen in yenem vinkl

00:17:06.074 --> 00:17:07.134
in Rige."

00:17:07.154 --> 00:17:09.022
iz im geven &lt;INTERESNO&gt;.

00:17:09.871 --> 00:17:11.744
&lt;Arn KAK RAZ POPADET&gt;.

00:17:11.744 --> 00:17:16.010
 er iz nokh geven gezunt mayn tate un un ales.

00:17:16.010 --> 00:17:19.787
dernokhdem, nokh der milkhome iz er farshlaft gevorn.

00:17:20.536 --> 00:17:22.859
m'hot im geshlogn. m'hot im gemutshet.

00:17:23.152 --> 00:17:25.272
nor yene yorn iz er geven

00:17:25.548 --> 00:17:27.669
geforn, gegan.

00:17:30.914 --> 00:17:32.680
vu iz geven dos ferd?

00:17:32.804 --> 00:17:36.151
dos ferd iz geven unter der, iz geven a magzon.

00:17:36.151 --> 00:17:38.332
unter der shtub iz geven a magzon.

00:17:38.332 --> 00:17:43.289
me, in a UNK dortn gekent makhn dortn tsvey KOMNATn, m'hot gekent zitsn.

00:17:43.289 --> 00:17:45.272
azoy hobn mir gehaltn dos ferd dort.

00:17:45.272 --> 00:17:50.197
mir hobn gehaltn koyln, mir hobn gehat holts. dortn &lt;fun dem alem&gt; vos me hot gedarft.

00:17:50.506 --> 00:17:52.157
iz geven a &lt;KHOD&gt;

00:17:52.194 --> 00:17:55.279
fun der shtub un m'hot nit gedarft geyn in droysn aroys.

00:17:55.279 --> 00:17:58.899
fun der shtub hobn mir farshme- farshlosn dem magazon

00:17:58.899 --> 00:18:05.649
az mir ho'mir arayngelozt dos ferd mit alemen, hot der tate farshlosn ineveynik, iz aribergegan in der shtub.

00:18:05.649 --> 00:18:08.320
ikh gedenk azoy, narishkeyt gedenkt zikh.

00:18:10.756 --> 00:18:11.729
&lt;un vayter&gt;.

00:18:12.967 --> 00:18:15.475
vu hot ir genemen esn gebn dos ferd?

00:18:15.785 --> 00:18:17.402
er hot gekoyft.

00:18:17.402 --> 00:18:19.029
fleg

00:18:19.029 --> 00:18:21.583
a &lt;tupen&gt; dos ferd untn,

00:18:21.583 --> 00:18:24.987
un s'hot zikh gepaset in a &lt;NA PRIMER UNK&gt;,

00:18:24.987 --> 00:18:28.880
un &lt;itster&gt; fleg er onkoyfn groz oyf vinter,

00:18:28.880 --> 00:18:32.598
sitshke fleg mayn tate, un gibn dem ferd esn.

00:18:32.598 --> 00:18:36.637
bay man tatn geven gibn &lt;dem&gt;, KHUDOBA esn gikher vi zikh.

00:18:37.554 --> 00:18:38.729
PERVAIA OCHERED'.

00:18:40.726 --> 00:18:43.623
oyf velekh loshn hot ir geredt in der heym?

00:18:43.645 --> 00:18:44.858
yidish.

00:18:45.924 --> 00:18:48.452
mayn tate, in dorf hot er geredt

00:18:48.452 --> 00:18:49.642
ukrainish

00:18:49.642 --> 00:18:54.460
un mayn t-, mame hot geredt yidish, ikh hob geredt yidish, mayn bruder hot geredt yidish.

00:18:54.460 --> 00:18:56.887
mir zenen gegan in a yidisher shkole.

00:18:58.242 --> 00:19:00.348
az me fleg ku-

00:19:00.348 --> 00:19:06.284
kumen di eltern oyf der SOBRANIE &lt;fleg men KHVALirn&gt; mayn mamen vos zi sh- shikt undz reyn,

00:19:06.284 --> 00:19:10.444
me, eynike flegn kumen, di kinder flegn kumen GRIAZNO

00:19:10.444 --> 00:19:16.597
un mayn mamen hot men &lt;KHVALet&gt; az zi shikt di kinder reyn, un vi a KHOZIAIKA. m'hot zi geKHVALyet.

00:19:25.209 --> 00:19:29.793
mm ir gedenkt, k- emetser fun di shkheynim?

00:19:30.642 --> 00:19:31.480
yo!

00:19:32.802 --> 00:19:36.762
yo, s'iz geven shkheynim, hobn zikh farhaltn zeyer gut.

00:19:36.633 --> 00:19:39.749
vi azoy hobn zey geheysn, un dertseylt a bisl fun zey.

00:19:38.253 --> 00:19:43.512
 eyne hot geheysn Sheve, di andere hot geheysn Rokhl,

00:19:45.121 --> 00:19:46.685
Pesye,

00:19:48.277 --> 00:19:50.600
&lt;geven&gt; a sakh shkheynim lebn undz.

00:19:51.382 --> 00:19:52.709
mit vos hobn zikh...

00:19:53.170 --> 00:19:55.561
der iz geven a shnayder,

00:19:55.837 --> 00:19:59.915
&lt;Khone&gt; shnayder; der iz geven azoy, der iz geven azoy.

00:20:00.781 --> 00:20:04.145
, geven azoy vi mayn tatn's

00:20:04.145 --> 00:20:08.667
 mayn tatn's SPETSIAL'NOST' gehat, oykhet ayngekoyft felekhlekh.

00:20:08.667 --> 00:20:11.975
m'hot opgefirt. mayn tate hot gearbet in VILSHINKI,

00:20:11.975 --> 00:20:15.811
un der yid hot gearbet in Me- in Meskivke.

00:20:21.385 --> 00:20:25.059
geven a natshalnik UNK keyn Krizhopil.

00:20:25.435 --> 00:20:27.691
fleg ikh PRINIMAYen ales.

00:20:28.135 --> 00:20:33.800
un mitn ferd fleg mayn tate opfirn shmates, felekhlekh, ales, a ful furl.

00:20:34.379 --> 00:20:35.001
ah

00:20:35.004 --> 00:20:42.029
az mir hobn gekontshet di shkole hot der tate &lt;hot&gt; mikh genemen keyn Krizhopil, geven bay &lt;mir&gt; a gedule, az der tate hot mikh genemen in

00:20:42.029 --> 00:20:43.570
in Krizhopil.

00:20:43.863 --> 00:20:46.063
hot mikh arayngefirt, hot mikh onge-

00:20:46.063 --> 00:20:48.633
ongehodevet in STOLOVA.

00:20:49.195 --> 00:20:51.088
iz geven a gedule in bod.

00:20:51.547 --> 00:20:54.196
veys, ikh bin geven a kind, kh'hob gornit gezen.

00:20:54.196 --> 00:20:56.193
az er hot mikh genemen, geven.

00:20:59.540 --> 00:21:03.635
ir zogt az er hot di shmates gefirt. vos hot er nokh gefirt?

00:21:03.759 --> 00:21:06.436
felekhlekh, shmates, ayzn.

00:21:06.965 --> 00:21:11.667
itstert hot men gefirt mit mashinen; demolt iz nit geven, nor mitn furl.

00:21:11.667 --> 00:21:15.997
vifl s'hot gekent aroyfgeyn oyfn furl hor der tate ongegreyt, hot avekgefirt.

00:21:15.997 --> 00:21:19.308
nokh a mol geforn, nokh a mol ongegreyt zikh.

00:21:18.929 --> 00:21:22.647
 vos heyst er hot ge- gefirt shmates un ayzn?

00:21:22.675 --> 00:21:25.893
 zogt, mir zoln farshteyn vos hey-

00:21:25.966 --> 00:21:27.952
vos heyst es, er hot gefirt...

00:21:27.114 --> 00:21:29.167
sh- shmates, ye.

00:21:28.132 --> 00:21:28.718
vi?

00:21:29.167 --> 00:21:36.252
ve-, alte shmates, veys nit. er iz geven a ZAGOTOVITEL' NA ETOGO. shmates, ayzn.

00:21:36.092 --> 00:21:36.836
vi-

00:21:36.252 --> 00:21:41.510
demolt iz geven dos o &lt;beyner&gt; oykhet PRINIMAYet. vos m'hot PRINIMAYet

00:21:41.510 --> 00:21:43.325
hot er oykhet PRINIMAYet.

00:21:43.027 --> 00:21:45.198
vu hot er genemen? anu, dertseylt.

00:21:44.748 --> 00:21:48.556
di, bay di goyim. di goyim hobn, flegn brengen

00:21:48.556 --> 00:21:52.067
sh- shkotsimlekh flegn brengen shmates; veys nit.

00:21:52.067 --> 00:21:55.939
m'hot zey gegibn v- tsvontsik kopekes, draysik kopekes, iz geven

00:21:55.939 --> 00:21:59.120
hobn zey geke- hobn zey gehat far vos tsu koyfn zikh.

00:21:59.682 --> 00:22:02.331
hot men gebrakht, hot der tate PRINIMAYet.

00:22:02.331 --> 00:22:05.671
der tate iz nit geven in der heym, hot di mame PRINIMAYet.

00:22:05.774 --> 00:22:11.590
zi iz geven a meyvn oyf di felekhlekh, hot zi PRINIMAY- flegn k- koylen a &lt;krolik&gt; oder

00:22:11.832 --> 00:22:15.826
a shmoys hot men ge- gekoylet, shmeyslekh.

00:22:16.135 --> 00:22:21.108
fleg der tate koyfn in dorf az, az me fleg brengen der mame, fleg di mame oykhet koyfn.

00:22:22.447 --> 00:22:24.753
zi iz geven a meyvn, fleg zi koyfn.

00:22:25.822 --> 00:22:28.584
un der tate fleg brengen funem dorf ales.

00:22:30.310 --> 00:22:32.195
un dernokhdem di shmeyslekh,

00:22:32.369 --> 00:22:34.962
&lt;vi no-&gt; hot er ge- ge- getun?

00:22:33.871 --> 00:22:35.823
gefirt keyn Krizhopil.

00:22:36.385 --> 00:22:38.185
ales hot men PRINIMAYet.

00:22:39.963 --> 00:22:42.151
er hot ge- vos hot er genemen

00:22:42.629 --> 00:22:43.990
far di shmeyslekh?

00:22:44.064 --> 00:22:45.040
ikh veys!

00:22:45.040 --> 00:22:49.509
oyf velkhe TSENA s'iz geven, azoy fil hot er genemen; azoy fil hot men gegibn.

00:22:49.700 --> 00:22:51.213
vos hot men gegebn?

00:22:50.763 --> 00:22:51.972
gelt!

00:22:52.552 --> 00:22:57.744
&lt;un az nit&gt; hot men im gegebn, demolt iz geven TRUDn, layvnt, hot er &lt;gebitn&gt;,

00:22:58.728 --> 00:23:04.691
nu, iz er geven, tsu yene yorn geven, vos iz geven TRUDn, layvnt, skhoyre.

00:23:04.702 --> 00:23:06.586
 ikh veys vos nokh.

00:23:07.570 --> 00:23:08.437
zhe-

00:23:08.437 --> 00:23:11.311
 shpilkes, nodlen,

00:23:16.818 --> 00:23:19.512
iz geven mayn tatn's &lt;profesye aza min&gt;.

00:23:20.294 --> 00:23:24.746
in yene tsaytn iz geven, hot er zikh, hot er nit gehat &lt;VOZMOZHNO&gt; zikh tsu lernen.

00:23:24.749 --> 00:23:27.658
iz er geven, der zeyde iz geven azoyner.

00:23:27.658 --> 00:23:32.000
hot ongenemen praktike. azoy iz der tate geven, azoy iz der zun geven.

00:23:34.672 --> 00:23:36.927
nu, dertseylt,

00:23:36.258 --> 00:23:43.677
un dernokhdem hot der DYADYA Srol zey farnemen, keyn, keyn Zhmerinke, &lt;zey&gt; zenen geforn keyn Tambov.

00:23:43.750 --> 00:23:46.107
DO VOINY zenen zey geforn.

00:23:46.062 --> 00:23:49.246
dertseylt, vi azoy iz bay aykh geven

00:23:49.353 --> 00:23:51.760
peysekh, zayt ir...

00:23:51.040 --> 00:23:53.704
peysekh flegn mir haltn peysekh.

00:23:52.053 --> 00:23:53.212
dertseylt.

00:23:53.704 --> 00:23:56.576
fleg kumen fraytik, fleg mayn tate kumen un

00:23:56.576 --> 00:23:58.268
un geyn in shul arayn.

00:23:58.268 --> 00:24:03.704
&lt;es&gt; fleg untergeyn a yontev, fleg er aheymkumen oyf a, oyfn yontev, &lt;zeyer&gt;.

00:24:03.967 --> 00:24:07.722
fleg, di mame fleg zeyer, nu ETOGO

00:24:07.722 --> 00:24:10.531
fleg haltn milekhdik gefes,

00:24:10.531 --> 00:24:14.382
fleyshedik gefes. a! zi hot gehat farshlaft gevorn

00:24:14.382 --> 00:24:18.288
un mi- mir zenen KH- KHOZIAIKAs geven mit mayn bruder.

00:24:18.344 --> 00:24:20.266
&lt;bay&gt; undz aroysgeyn in mark,

00:24:20.266 --> 00:24:21.957
fleysh shoyn, hot zi gev-

00:24:21.957 --> 00:24:24.266
hot er gekoyft SVININA-fleysh. a!

00:24:24.266 --> 00:24:27.436
gekumen, hot di mame aroysgevorfn di POSUDA

00:24:27.436 --> 00:24:28.957
mitn fleysh.

00:24:29.357 --> 00:24:31.377
un hot undz azoy geshlogn.

00:24:31.377 --> 00:24:32.125
zogn

00:24:33.684 --> 00:24:35.062
&lt;un hot undz&gt;, a!

00:24:35.574 --> 00:24:37.458
zogn "du &lt;veyst&gt; vos tsu tun"!

00:24:39.961 --> 00:24:42.082
anu, dertseylt, vi azoy hot ir ge-

00:24:42.340 --> 00:24:45.170
peysekh in der heym, vi azoy iz geven peysekh?

00:24:43.707 --> 00:24:47.803
mayn mame hot gebakn akht teg, ale tog hot zi gebakn.

00:24:47.803 --> 00:24:51.122
un matses hobn mir opgebakn tsvey pud matses.

00:24:51.122 --> 00:24:54.397
un gebakn farfl un gemakht matse-mel.

00:24:54.397 --> 00:24:55.912
ale tog hobn mir gebakn.

00:24:55.912 --> 00:24:59.521
peysekhdike pletslekh. ales iz geven.

00:25:00.042 --> 00:25:00.695
DA.

00:25:00.700 --> 00:25:04.795
nu, dertseylt, vi azoy iz geven a- bay aykh peysekh in der shtub?

00:25:03.535 --> 00:25:05.785
peysekh azo-, in der shtub.

00:25:04.795 --> 00:25:05.429
z-

00:25:05.785 --> 00:25:08.173
mir hobn gehat peysekhdik gefes.

00:25:08.173 --> 00:25:10.229
hot di mame aropgenemen

00:25:10.420 --> 00:25:13.193
un hot es oysge- oysgevashn,

00:25:13.193 --> 00:25:18.671
un eynike zakhn iz geven, hot zi oysgekashert, arayngevorfn in oyvn arayn un oysgekashert.

00:25:18.671 --> 00:25:21.544
opgebrotn kartoflyes mir hobn geesn.

00:25:21.544 --> 00:25:23.139
ikh gedenk azoy vi haynt.

00:25:24.207 --> 00:25:26.632
vos s'hot zikh, iz &lt;dos&gt; geven peysekh.

00:25:25.608 --> 00:25:27.340
vos iz geven oyfn tish?

00:25:27.110 --> 00:25:28.336
vos s'iz geven.

00:25:28.477 --> 00:25:31.475
u- oyfes hobn mir ongegreyt,

00:25:31.582 --> 00:25:34.073
un fleysh hobn mir genemen.

00:25:34.073 --> 00:25:37.891
fish hobn mir genemen. mir hobn ales opgebakn, &lt;a banke&gt; rosl,

00:25:37.891 --> 00:25:39.130
ales iz geven.

00:25:39.130 --> 00:25:41.263
bay tog, der tate iz gekumen,

00:25:41.263 --> 00:25:47.624
hobn mir geesn &lt;a banke&gt; rosl; dernokhdem iz der tate gekumen fun der shul, hobn mir geesn a yoykh.

00:25:47.680 --> 00:25:49.838
azoy o, balebatish iz geven.

00:25:49.838 --> 00:25:54.446
oreme melukhe, nor a freylekhe melukhe. zogt men a mol dos vertl.

00:25:54.446 --> 00:25:57.532
a oreme melukhe nor a freylekh-

00:25:58.722 --> 00:25:59.808
vi hot ge-

00:26:00.944 --> 00:26:02.896
gedavnt der tate hot zikh ge-

00:26:02.210 --> 00:26:08.054
der tate, yo, hot gedavnt, er fleg oyfshteyn in der fri, er iz geven in der heym, hot er opgedavnt, do hot er

00:26:08.054 --> 00:26:10.138
zikh genemen dem tales

00:26:10.141 --> 00:26:17.449
in mitn, un avekgegan in shul arayn un hot er gedavnt in shul. do iz er gekumen a mol, hot men opgegesn.

00:26:17.449 --> 00:26:19.109
mayn mame hot nit ge-

00:26:19.109 --> 00:26:21.619
&lt;geflegt&gt; kumen oyf shabes, fleg zi

00:26:21.619 --> 00:26:24.300
opkokhn fish, opkokhn KHOLODNYE

00:26:24.300 --> 00:26:27.233
 un zi fleg keyn fayer nit makhn

00:26:27.233 --> 00:26:28.006
shabes.

00:26:29.142 --> 00:26:31.823
keyn fayer iz nit geven. itstert iz men

00:26:31.823 --> 00:26:34.081
makht men a fayer, makht men ales.

00:26:33.985 --> 00:26:36.421
a velkhn nokh yontev hot ir

00:26:36.421 --> 00:26:37.321
gedenkt,

00:26:37.749 --> 00:26:39.059
velkhn nokh yontev?

00:26:38.052 --> 00:26:41.593
sh- shvues flegn mir haltn.

00:26:41.593 --> 00:26:43.500
fleg mayn mame opbakn

00:26:43.500 --> 00:26:46.926
fun rayz knishes,

00:26:46.926 --> 00:26:50.298
fun hirzh knishes, fun kez knishes.

00:26:50.675 --> 00:26:55.749
un opbakn koyletshn, oysflekhtn oyf k- oyf shvues.

00:26:56.362 --> 00:26:59.866
azoy balebatish. vi azoy zi hot gezen bay ire eltern.

00:27:00.024 --> 00:27:04.203
mayn mm mayn tate iz geven a gemeyner yunger-man,

00:27:04.293 --> 00:27:06.847
un fun oreme eltern iz er aroys.

00:27:06.847 --> 00:27:08.619
un mayn mame's eltern

00:27:08.630 --> 00:27:10.632
iz geven raykhe eltern.

00:27:11.262 --> 00:27:12.759
a balebatishe.

00:27:12.967 --> 00:27:16.100
nor iz oysgerisn gevorn far fri mayn zeyde.

00:27:18.198 --> 00:27:20.330
a velkhe nokh, pe-

00:27:20.358 --> 00:27:22.360
yontev ir gedenkt?

00:27:23.075 --> 00:27:27.085
NA PRIMER itstert o SUDNYI DEN'.

00:27:23.085 --> 00:27:24.085
vi azoy UNK

00:27:27.564 --> 00:27:29.110
vi azoy iz oyf yidish?

00:27:30.522 --> 00:27:36.535
me po- &lt;me fort&gt; yonkiper, rosheshone, sukes,

00:27:37.908 --> 00:27:43.319
simkhes-toyre; se tsit zikh a gantsn khoydesh der yontev.

00:27:44.911 --> 00:27:46.908
nu, ir gedenkt

00:27:46.908 --> 00:27:48.266
far di kinder

00:27:48.303 --> 00:27:50.170
a velkhe geven yontev

00:27:51.841 --> 00:27:53.039
vos far di kin-

00:27:52.247 --> 00:27:54.231
vos m'hot nokh gelt gegebn?

00:27:54.243 --> 00:27:56.349
khanike, a!

00:27:55.053 --> 00:27:56.802
anu, dertseylt. der-

00:27:56.352 --> 00:28:01.596
flegn shkheynim mir gebn, kumen DYADYA S- Srol fleg er mir gebn, DYADYA Yosl.

00:28:01.596 --> 00:28:04.958
der tate fleg kumen funem dorf. "na, Khanele."

00:28:05.698 --> 00:28:12.209
a-, er hot gehat a &lt;velt&gt;, fleg ikh a mol mit im forn keyn, keyn Krizhopil mitn furl.

00:28:13.143 --> 00:28:18.250
&lt;a&gt;, s'iz geven a gedule in bod. frier &lt;hot es n-&gt;, keyn mashinen nit geforn azoy.

00:28:18.442 --> 00:28:21.527
mit furlekh iz men, iz men geforn.

00:28:21.547 --> 00:28:24.170
fleg mayn tate afile forn keyn Krizhopil

00:28:24.170 --> 00:28:26.989
un farnemen...

00:28:26.989 --> 00:28:29.372
me fleg onkumen zumer,

00:28:29.377 --> 00:28:31.801
fleg er nemen pasazhirn.

00:28:35.047 --> 00:28:37.724
abi me fleg im rufn, fleg er forn.

00:28:38.962 --> 00:28:41.381
fleg men im batsoln un er fleg forn,

00:28:41.409 --> 00:28:42.264
mayn tate.

00:28:42.235 --> 00:28:44.626
vu hot di mame gekokht un gebakn?

00:28:44.919 --> 00:28:48.794
gekokht un gebakn? a oyvn iz geven.

00:28:49.002 --> 00:28:50.746
vinter in der rube.

00:28:50.746 --> 00:28:52.659
zumer oyf der trinozhke.

00:28:54.588 --> 00:28:56.560
dernokhdem hobn mir shoyn gekoyft a

00:28:56.560 --> 00:29:02.421
a &lt;STOL'NAIA&gt; plitke un a balon, hobn mir gekokht, NA GAZ.

00:29:02.421 --> 00:29:05.368
ah, yene yorn in a trinozhke.

00:29:05.368 --> 00:29:07.191
NA pripetshik, m'iz...

00:29:07.191 --> 00:29:08.116
UNK

00:29:08.307 --> 00:29:09.685
hob ikh gekokht.

00:29:13.117 --> 00:29:14.866
 VSYO.

00:29:20.761 --> 00:29:22.342
mir veln zikh bald

00:29:22.465 --> 00:29:23.827
opshteln

00:29:25.030 --> 00:29:26.898
un vayter farshraybn

00:29:27.039 --> 00:29:28.957
oyf di tsveyte KASETE.

00:29:29.199 --> 00:29:30.206
KHOROSHO.
